Class Summary.Child

    @ThreadSafe
public class Summary.Child
extends Object
implements Metric.Child

    A concrete instance of Summary for a unique set of label dimensions.

    Warning: Do not hold onto a reference of a Summary.Child if you ever use the Metric.resetAll(). If you want to hold onto a concrete instance, please hold onto a Summary.Partial and use Summary.Partial.apply().
